				<td colspan="2"><span>For level 65s, I'm pretty sure the physical trap in the Tower of Frozen Shadow still works.  Not positive about that though.  But yes, mobs must be at least light blue to get any kind of combat skill-ups from them.
<br />

<br />
My Defense is at or near max for my level from pulling and crowd controlling in groups.  Imho, that is the best way to do it.  If the skill is way behind from too much kiting or PLing, for example, these other methods are certainly useful.  Getting hit in group situations when your Defense already sucks is a mana drain on your healer, unfortunately.</span></td>
